#. type: Content of: <html><body><h1>
#: l10n/build/help.html.in:6 l10n/build/help.html.in:41
msgid "MX Updater Help"
msgstr "Aide de MX Updater"

#. type: Content of: <html><body><p>
#: l10n/build/help.html.in:43
msgid ""
"MX Updater monitors your MX Linux system for available package updates and "
"shows a tray icon reflecting the current status. Desktop notifications can "
"also be shown when updates become available."
msgstr ""
"MX Updater surveille votre systeme MX Linux pour les mises a jour de paquets "
"disponibles et affiche une icone dans la zone de notification indiquant "
"l'etat actuel. Des notifications de bureau peuvent egalement etre affichees "
"lorsque des mises a jour sont disponibles."

#. type: Content of: <html><body><p>
#: l10n/build/help.html.in:47
msgid ""
"Personal preferences can be adjusted by opening <b>MX Updater Preferences</"
"b> from MX Tools, the System Menu, or the right-click menu of the tray icon."
msgstr ""
"Les preferences personnelles peuvent etre ajustees en ouvrant les "
"<b>Preferences de MX Updater</b> depuis MX Tools, le menu Systeme ou le menu "
"contextuel de l'icone dans la zone de notification."

#. type: Attribute 'alt' of: <html><body><div><img>
#: l10n/build/help.html.in:50
msgid "Settings window"
msgstr "Fenetre des parametres"

#. type: Content of: <html><body><h2>
#: l10n/build/help.html.in:51
msgid "Upgrade Mode"
msgstr "Mode de mise a jour"

#. type: Content of: <html><body><p>
#: l10n/build/help.html.in:53
msgid "Controls the upgrade method and schedule:"
msgstr "Controle la methode de mise a jour et le calendrier :"

#. type: Content of: <html><body><ul><li>
#: l10n/build/help.html.in:55
msgid ""
"%%FULL%% (recommended) -- upgrades packages and allows installing or "
"removing packages where needed to satisfy dependencies."
msgstr ""
"%%FULL%% (recommande) -- met a jour les paquets et autorise l'installation "
"ou la suppression de paquets si necessaire pour satisfaire les dependances."

#. type: Content of: <html><body><ul><li>
#: l10n/build/help.html.in:57
msgid ""
"%%BASIC%% -- upgrades packages but will not install new ones or remove "
"existing ones. Safer, but some packages may be kept back."
msgstr ""
"%%BASIC%% -- met a jour les paquets mais n'en installe pas de nouveaux ni ne "
"supprime les existants. Plus sur, mais certains paquets peuvent etre retenus."

#. type: Content of: <html><body><ul><li>
#: l10n/build/help.html.in:59
msgid ""
"<b>Nala</b> -- when checked, uses Nala instead of apt as the package manager "
"(only shown if Nala is installed)."
msgstr ""
"<b>Nala</b> -- si coche, utilise Nala a la place d'apt comme gestionnaire de "
"paquets (affiche uniquement si Nala est installe)."

#. type: Content of: <html><body><p>
#: l10n/build/help.html.in:62
msgid ""
"The %%REFRESH%% dropdown sets how often the package list is fetched from the "
"servers (daily, every 3 days, weekly, every 2 weeks, monthly, or never).  "
"The %%AUTOMATIC%% checkbox enables unattended upgrades on the same schedule."
msgstr ""
"La liste deroulante %%REFRESH%% definit la frequence de recuperation de la "
"liste de paquets depuis les serveurs (quotidien, tous les 3 jours, "
"hebdomadaire, toutes les 2 semaines, mensuel ou jamais). La case a cocher %"
"%AUTOMATIC%% active les mises a jour automatiques selon le meme calendrier."

#. type: Content of: <html><body><h2>
#: l10n/build/help.html.in:66
msgid "Left-Click"
msgstr "Clic gauche"

#. type: Content of: <html><body><p>
#: l10n/build/help.html.in:68
msgid ""
"Choose what happens when you left-click the tray icon. Available choices "
"depend on which applications are installed:"
msgstr ""
"Choisissez ce qui se passe lorsque vous cliquez avec le bouton gauche sur "
"l'icone de notification. Les choix disponibles dependent des applications "
"installees :"

#. type: Content of: <html><body><ul><li>
#: l10n/build/help.html.in:71
msgid ""
"%%VIEW_AND_UPGRADE%% (default) -- opens the MX Updater upgrade window when "
"updates are available; falls back to the first installed package manager "
"otherwise."
msgstr ""
"%%VIEW_AND_UPGRADE%% (par defaut) -- ouvre la fenetre de mise a jour de MX "
"Updater lorsque des mises a jour sont disponibles ; revient au premier "
"gestionnaire de paquets installe sinon."

#. type: Content of: <html><body><ul><li>
#: l10n/build/help.html.in:73
msgid ""
"<b>Synaptic</b> -- opens Synaptic Package Manager (always, with or without "
"updates)."
msgstr ""
"<b>Synaptic</b> -- ouvre Synaptic Package Manager (toujours, avec ou sans "
"mises a jour)."

#. type: Content of: <html><body><ul><li>
#: l10n/build/help.html.in:74
msgid ""
"<b>MX Package Installer</b> -- opens MX Package Installer (always, with or "
"without updates)."
msgstr ""
"<b>MX Package Installer</b> -- ouvre MX Package Installer (toujours, avec ou "
"sans mises a jour)."

#. type: Content of: <html><body><p>
#: l10n/build/help.html.in:76
msgid ""
"Middle-clicking the tray icon always opens MX Package Installer, regardless "
"of the left-click setting."
msgstr ""
"Un clic avec le bouton central sur l'icone de notification ouvre toujours MX "
"Package Installer, quelle que soit la configuration du clic gauche."

#. type: Content of: <html><body><h3>
#: l10n/build/help.html.in:79
msgid "Right-Click Menu"
msgstr "Menu du clic droit"

#. type: Content of: <html><body><p>
#: l10n/build/help.html.in:81
msgid ""
"Right-clicking the tray icon opens the context menu. Entries are only shown "
"when the corresponding application is installed or condition applies:"
msgstr ""
"Un clic droit sur l'icone de notification ouvre le menu contextuel. Les "
"entrees ne sont affichees que si l'application correspondante est installee "
"ou si la condition est remplie :"

#. type: Content of: <html><body><ul><li>
#: l10n/build/help.html.in:84
msgid ""
"%%VIEW_AND_UPGRADE%% -- open the upgrade window (shown when updates are "
"available)."
msgstr ""
"%%VIEW_AND_UPGRADE%% -- ouvre la fenetre de mise a jour (affichee lorsque "
"des mises a jour sont disponibles)."

#. type: Content of: <html><body><ul><li>
#: l10n/build/help.html.in:85
msgid "<b>Synaptic</b> -- open Synaptic Package Manager."
msgstr "<b>Synaptic</b> -- ouvre Synaptic Package Manager."

#. type: Content of: <html><body><ul><li>
#: l10n/build/help.html.in:86
msgid "<b>MX Package Installer</b> -- open MX Package Installer."
msgstr "<b>MX Package Installer</b> -- ouvre MX Package Installer."

#. type: Content of: <html><body><ul><li>
#: l10n/build/help.html.in:87
msgid "<b>MX Repo Manager</b> -- open MX Repo Manager."
msgstr "<b>MX Repo Manager</b> -- ouvre MX Repo Manager."

#. type: Content of: <html><body><ul><li>
#: l10n/build/help.html.in:88
msgid ""
"%%CHECK_FOR_UPDATES%% -- open a terminal and fetch the latest package lists "
"from the servers."
msgstr ""
"%%CHECK_FOR_UPDATES%% -- ouvre un terminal et recupere les dernieres listes "
"de paquets depuis les serveurs."

#. type: Content of: <html><body><ul><li>
#: l10n/build/help.html.in:89
msgid ""
"%%HISTORY%% -- open MX Updater History to view recently installed or removed "
"packages."
msgstr ""
"%%HISTORY%% -- ouvre l'historique de MX Updater pour afficher les paquets "
"recemment installes ou supprimes."

#. type: Content of: <html><body><ul><li>
#: l10n/build/help.html.in:90
msgid "%%AUTO_UPDATE_LOGS%% -- view the log of automatic upgrades."
msgstr ""
"%%AUTO_UPDATE_LOGS%% -- affiche le journal des mises a jour automatiques."

#. type: Content of: <html><body><ul><li>
#: l10n/build/help.html.in:91
msgid "%%AUTO_UPDATE_DPKG_LOGS%% -- view the dpkg log of automatic upgrades."
msgstr ""
"%%AUTO_UPDATE_DPKG_LOGS%% -- affiche le journal dpkg des mises a jour "
"automatiques."

#. type: Content of: <html><body><ul><li>
#: l10n/build/help.html.in:92
msgid "%%HELP%% -- this document."
msgstr "%%HELP%% -- ce document."

#. type: Content of: <html><body><ul><li>
#: l10n/build/help.html.in:93
msgid "%%PREFERENCES%% -- open the MX Updater Preferences window."
msgstr "%%PREFERENCES%% -- ouvre la fenetre des preferences de MX Updater."

#. type: Content of: <html><body><ul><li>
#: l10n/build/help.html.in:94
msgid "%%ABOUT%% -- version information, license and changelog."
msgstr ""
"%%ABOUT%% -- informations de version, licence et journal des modifications."

#. type: Content of: <html><body><ul><li>
#: l10n/build/help.html.in:95
msgid ""
"%%RESTART_MX_UPDATER%% -- restart the tray icon process. Useful after manual "
"configuration changes; will show a notification if updates are available."
msgstr ""
"%%RESTART_MX_UPDATER%% -- redemarre le processus de l'icone de notification. "
"Utile apres des modifications manuelles de la configuration ; affiche une "
"notification si des mises a jour sont disponibles."

#. type: Content of: <html><body><ul><li>
#: l10n/build/help.html.in:97
msgid ""
"%%HIDE_WHEN_NO_UPDATES%% -- only shown when the system is up to date; "
"toggles whether the tray icon is hidden when there are no updates (not "
"available on KDE)."
msgstr ""
"%%HIDE_WHEN_NO_UPDATES%% -- affiche uniquement quand le systeme est a jour ; "
"bascule l'affichage de l'icone de notification lorsqu'il n'y a pas de mises "
"a jour (non disponible sous KDE)."

#. type: Content of: <html><body><ul><li>
#: l10n/build/help.html.in:99
msgid "%%QUIT%% -- close MX Updater."
msgstr "%%QUIT%% -- ferme MX Updater."

#. type: Content of: <html><body><h2>
#: l10n/build/help.html.in:102
msgid "Icons"
msgstr "Icones"

#. type: Content of: <html><body><p>
#: l10n/build/help.html.in:104
msgid ""
"Choose the icon set used in the system tray. Each set shows two icons: the "
"left icon is used when updates are available, the right icon when the system "
"is up to date."
msgstr ""
"Choisissez le jeu d'icones utilise dans la zone de notification. Chaque jeu "
"affiche deux icones : l'icone de gauche est utilisee lorsque des mises a "
"jour sont disponibles, celle de droite lorsque le systeme est a jour."

#. type: Content of: <html><body><p>
#: l10n/build/help.html.in:107
msgid ""
"Note: with %%BASIC_UPGRADE%% selected, packages that would require "
"installing or removing other packages are kept back. When all remaining "
"updates are such kept-back packages the up-to-date (right) icon is shown."
msgstr ""
"Remarque : avec %%BASIC_UPGRADE%% selectionne, les paquets qui "
"necessiteraient l'installation ou la suppression d'autres paquets sont "
"retenus. Lorsque toutes les mises a jour restantes sont de tels paquets "
"retenus, l'icone a jour (droite) est affichee."

#. type: Content of: <html><body><p>
#: l10n/build/help.html.in:110
msgid ""
"The %%TRANSPARENT_WIREFRAME%% toggle makes the no-updates icon transparent "
"with either black or white wire lines. Use black wires on a light panel, "
"white wires on a dark panel, so the icon does not disappear into the panel "
"background."
msgstr ""
"Le bouton %%TRANSPARENT_WIREFRAME%% rend l'icone 'aucune mise a jour' "
"transparente avec des traits noirs ou blancs. Utilisez des traits noirs sur "
"un panneau clair, blancs sur un panneau sombre, afin que l'icone ne se fonde "
"pas dans l'arriere-plan du panneau."

#. type: Content of: <html><body><p>
#: l10n/build/help.html.in:114
msgid ""
"A local administrator can define a custom icon set by placing a "
"configuration file at <code>/usr/local/etc/mx-updater.conf</code>. An "
"example with full documentation is provided in <a href=\"file:///usr/share/"
"doc/mx-updater/examples/admin-mx-updater.conf\">/usr/share/doc/mx-updater/"
"examples/admin-mx-updater.conf</a>."
msgstr ""
"Un administrateur local peut definir un jeu d'icones personnalise en placant "
"un fichier de configuration dans <code>/usr/local/etc/mx-updater.conf</"
"code>. Un exemple avec la documentation complete est fourni dans <a "
"href=\"file:///usr/share/doc/mx-updater/examples/admin-mx-updater.conf\">/"
"usr/share/doc/mx-updater/examples/admin-mx-updater.conf</a>."

#. type: Content of: <html><body><h2>
#: l10n/build/help.html.in:119
msgid "Other"
msgstr "Autre"

#. type: Content of: <html><body><p>
#: l10n/build/help.html.in:121
msgid ""
"Most entries in this section have a tooltip with further details -- hover "
"over the label to read it."
msgstr ""
"La plupart des entrees de cette section ont une info-bulle avec des details "
"supplementaires -- survolez le libelle avec la souris pour la lire."

#. type: Content of: <html><body><ul><li>
#: l10n/build/help.html.in:124
msgid ""
"%%TERMINAL_SIZE%% -- size of the terminal window that opens during "
"upgrades.  Options: <i>default</i> (2/3 of screen, capped at 960x600 on wide "
"displays), <i>one-third</i>, <i>half</i>, <i>two-thirds</i>, <i>three-"
"quarters</i>, <i>nine-tenths</i>, or <i>own</i> (no size hint -- the "
"terminal uses its own saved size and position)."
msgstr ""
"%%TERMINAL_SIZE%% -- taille de la fenetre terminal qui s'ouvre pendant les "
"mises a jour. Options : <i>default</i> (2/3 de l'ecran, plafonne a 960x600 "
"sur les grands ecrans), <i>one-third</i>, <i>half</i>, <i>two-thirds</i>, "
"<i>three-quarters</i>, <i>nine-tenths</i> ou <i>own</i> (aucune indication "
"de taille -- le terminal utilise sa propre taille et position enregistrees)."

#. type: Content of: <html><body><ul><li>
#: l10n/build/help.html.in:129
msgid ""
"%%POSITION%% -- screen position of the terminal window: center, top-left, "
"top-right, bottom-left, or bottom-right. Not available on Wayland or when "
"size is set to <i>own</i>."
msgstr ""
"%%POSITION%% -- position a l'ecran de la fenetre terminal : centre, haut-"
"gauche, haut-droite, bas-gauche ou bas-droite. Non disponible sous Wayland "
"ou lorsque la taille est definie sur <i>own</i>."

#. type: Content of: <html><body><ul><li>
#: l10n/build/help.html.in:132
msgid ""
"%%SKIP_UPGRADE_CONFIRMATION%% -- passes <code>--assume-yes</code> to apt or "
"Nala, automatically answering yes to the \"Do you want to continue?\" "
"prompt.  Note: configuration questions from individual package scripts "
"(debconf) may still appear -- this is normal and not controlled by this "
"setting.  Use with care: on a yes answer apt will proceed even if the "
"upgrade would remove packages to resolve a dependency conflict."
msgstr ""
"%%SKIP_UPGRADE_CONFIRMATION%% -- passe <code>--assume-yes</code> a apt ou "
"Nala, repondant automatiquement oui a l'invite \"Voulez-vous continuer ?\". "
"Remarque : les questions de configuration des scripts de paquets individuels "
"(debconf) peuvent toujours apparaitre -- c'est normal et non controle par ce "
"parametre. A utiliser avec precaution : avec une reponse oui, apt continuera "
"meme si la mise a jour devait supprimer des paquets pour resoudre un conflit "
"de dependance."

#. type: Content of: <html><body><ul><li>
#: l10n/build/help.html.in:138
msgid ""
"%%DESKTOP_NOTIFICATIONS%% -- show a desktop notification when updates become "
"available."
msgstr ""
"%%DESKTOP_NOTIFICATIONS%% -- affiche une notification de bureau lorsque des "
"mises a jour deviennent disponibles."

#. type: Content of: <html><body><ul><li>
#: l10n/build/help.html.in:140
msgid ""
"%%AUTOSTART_DELAY%% -- wait a short time after login before starting, so the "
"desktop is fully set up before MX Updater appears in the tray."
msgstr ""
"%%AUTOSTART_DELAY%% -- attend un court instant apres la connexion avant de "
"demarrer, afin que le bureau soit entierement configure avant que MX Updater "
"n'apparaisse dans la zone de notification."

#. type: Content of: <html><body><ul><li>
#: l10n/build/help.html.in:142
msgid ""
"%%HIDE_WHEN_NO_UPDATES%% -- hide the tray icon when the system is up to "
"date. Not available on KDE/Plasma."
msgstr ""
"%%HIDE_WHEN_NO_UPDATES%% -- masque l'icone de notification lorsque le "
"systeme est a jour. Non disponible sous KDE/Plasma."

#. type: Content of: <html><body><h2>
#: l10n/build/help.html.in:146
msgid "Authentication"
msgstr "Authentification"

#. type: Content of: <html><body><p>
#: l10n/build/help.html.in:148
msgid ""
"Authentication is required to upgrade packages. A password prompt will "
"appear."
msgstr ""
"Une authentification est requise pour mettre a jour les paquets. Une invite "
"de mot de passe s'affichera."

#. type: Content of: <html><body><h2>
#: l10n/build/help.html.in:150
msgid "Troubleshooting"
msgstr "Depannage"

#. type: Content of: <html><body><h3>
#: l10n/build/help.html.in:152
msgid "The tray icon does not appear"
msgstr "L'icone de notification n'apparait pas"

#. type: Content of: <html><body><p>
#: l10n/build/help.html.in:153
msgid ""
"MX Updater starts automatically at login via an XDG autostart entry "
"installed with the package. If the icon is missing it can be started "
"manually from <b>MX Tools</b> or the <b>System Menu</b>. On some desktops "
"the system tray area must be added to the panel manually."
msgstr ""
"MX Updater demarre automatiquement a la connexion via une entree de "
"demarrage automatique XDG installee avec le paquet. Si l'icone est absente, "
"il peut etre demarre manuellement depuis <b>MX Tools</b> ou le <b>menu "
"Systeme</b>. Sur certains bureaux, la zone de notification doit etre ajoutee "
"manuellement au panneau."

#. type: Content of: <html><body><h3>
#: l10n/build/help.html.in:158
msgid "A password is asked every time I click Upgrade"
msgstr ""
"Un mot de passe est demande chaque fois que je clique sur Mettre a jour"

#. type: Content of: <html><body><p>
#: l10n/build/help.html.in:159
msgid "This is expected -- authentication is always required for upgrades."
msgstr ""
"C'est le comportement attendu -- l'authentification est toujours requise "
"pour les mises a jour."

#. type: Content of: <html><body><h3>
#: l10n/build/help.html.in:161
msgid "Updates are not detected"
msgstr "Les mises a jour ne sont pas detectees"

#. type: Content of: <html><body><p>
#: l10n/build/help.html.in:162
msgid ""
"Use %%CHECK_FOR_UPDATES%% from the right-click menu to force an immediate "
"check. The terminal window will show any errors, including a locked apt "
"database from another running package manager."
msgstr ""
"Utilisez %%CHECK_FOR_UPDATES%% dans le menu du clic droit pour forcer une "
"verification immediate. La fenetre terminal affichera toutes les erreurs, y "
"compris une base de donnees apt verrouillee par un autre gestionnaire de "
"paquets en cours d'execution."

#. type: Content of: <html><body><h3>
#: l10n/build/help.html.in:166
msgid "The upgrade window shows no packages"
msgstr "La fenetre de mise a jour n'affiche aucun paquet"

#. type: Content of: <html><body><p>
#: l10n/build/help.html.in:167
msgid ""
"Your system is up to date, or the last check has not completed yet.  Use %"
"%CHECK_FOR_UPDATES%% to refresh."
msgstr ""
"Votre systeme est a jour, ou la derniere verification n'est pas encore "
"terminee. Utilisez %%CHECK_FOR_UPDATES%% pour actualiser."

